stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> START
    
    START --> LLM_CALL: Initialize MessagesState
    
    LLM_CALL: llm_call Node
    note right of LLM_CALL
        - Prepends SystemMessage
        - Invokes LLM with tools bound
        - Returns AIMessage (may contain tool_calls)
        - Increments llm_calls counter
    end note
    
    LLM_CALL --> CHECK: AIMessage returned
    
    CHECK: should_continue()
    note right of CHECK
        Checks if last message:
        - Is AIMessage
        - Has tool_calls
    end note
    
    CHECK --> TOOL_NODE: Has tool_calls
    CHECK --> END: No tool_calls
    
    TOOL_NODE: tool_node
    note right of TOOL_NODE
        - Extracts tool_calls from AIMessage
        - Executes each tool
        - Returns ToolMessage(s) with results
        - Handles JSON serialization
    end note
    
    TOOL_NODE --> LLM_CALL: ToolMessage(s) added to state
    
    END --> [*]
